---
title: Lamb Pasta Bake with Rosemary and Spinach
description: In Britain, rosemary is a traditional symbol of love and marriage. Brides once adorned their veils with it - a precursor to the modern bouquet. Show your family some love with this superquick and tasty dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lamb-pasta-bake-a24f94dd-dad6af6f.jpg
